cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of generating realistic and diverse images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The proposed method involves regularization and optimization techniques, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper focuses on generating images with multiple modalities, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
